      • createStaticInstance

        public static KawapadFrame createStaticInstance()
        Kawapad#init() must be called whenever any Kawapad instance is created. Due to INIT_03 (see the comment in the source code), the constructor cannot call this method directory; we decided to mandate the users to call this method manually.
